txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Albino skin taken from the beasts in the areas around Echad Dúnann. Deliver the items to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann.
'We will make good use of these. Thank you.'
'We have many uses for the skin, fur, and ears of the beasts from these lands.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Albino Skin
Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann has requested that a collection of albino skin be delivered to her.
Deliver the albino skin to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann in Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver albino skin from the beasts found near Echad Dúnann to the Elf-maid Tinúriel. Tinúriel can be found in Echad Dúnann.
Wanted: Albino skin taken from the beasts in the areas around Echad Dúnann.
